Package: rieszreg
Type: Package
Title: Shared Abstractions for Riesz Regression
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Alejandro", "Schuler", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                    email = "aschuler@berkeley.edu"))
Description: Shared estimand factories, Bregman-Riesz losses, and the
    base R6 estimator class used by every implementation package in the
    RieszReg family (rieszboost, krrr, future). Implementation packages
    add concrete backends and convenience subclasses; this package holds
    the abstractions they share.
License: TBD
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    R6,
    reticulate (>= 1.30)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    pkgload
SystemRequirements: Python (>= 3.10), the Python package 'rieszreg'
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
